- No.

01:35:34.056 --> 01:35:39.187
No, you don't...
not really.

01:35:41.930 --> 01:35:45.264
You see, the truth is...

01:35:45.334 --> 01:35:47.460
I gave my heart away
a long time ago...

01:35:48.636 --> 01:35:51.070
My whole heart...

01:35:51.139 --> 01:35:53.607
and I never really
got it back.

01:35:53.675 --> 01:35:58.637
And I don't even know what
else to say, but I'm sorry.

01:35:58.780 --> 01:36:00.441
I can't marry you.

01:36:07.487 --> 01:36:09.978
And you shouldn't want
to marry me.

01:36:18.832 --> 01:36:21.801
So this
is what this feels like.

01:36:23.737 --> 01:36:26.228
That's it?!

01:36:26.306 --> 01:36:28.330
You're just gonna
let her humiliate you...

01:36:28.407 --> 01:36:31.035
with some bullshit
about an old husband?!

01:36:52.397 --> 01:36:54.863
Yeah, I think I am.

01:37:01.272 --> 01:37:03.297
Excuse me.

01:37:13.150 --> 01:37:16.017
In my entire life...

01:37:16.086 --> 01:37:20.887
I have never met anyone
so manipulative, so deceitful!

01:37:22.092 --> 01:37:23.389
And I'm in politics!

01:37:23.560 --> 01:37:25.428
I'm just trying to be honest.

01:37:25.496 --> 01:37:29.687
I will not allow the future
President of the United States...

01:37:29.799 --> 01:37:33.166
