by some psycho Daisy Mae!

01:37:33.236 --> 01:37:35.500
You go after him,
you little bitch!

01:37:36.171 --> 01:37:38.267
Wait just a minute, missy.

01:37:38.341 --> 01:37:40.775
Uh, there... there's no need
for name-callin', now.

01:37:40.843 --> 01:37:44.074
Now, she spoke her piece,
and that's all there is to it.

01:37:44.147 --> 01:37:48.873
Oh, go back to your double-wide
and fry something.

01:37:58.827 --> 01:38:01.227
Nobody talks
to my mama like that!

01:38:01.296 --> 01:38:04.356
Praise the Lord!
The South has risen again!

01:38:16.911 --> 01:38:18.845
If you're friends of the bride,
stick around!

01:38:18.913 --> 01:38:20.847
I'm gonna go find me
