01:39:15.733 --> 01:39:16.927
Hey, cowboy...

01:39:22.340 --> 01:39:24.308
You owe me a dance.

01:39:24.375 --> 01:39:27.435
Nice dress.
Where's your husband?

01:39:27.512 --> 01:39:29.503
I'm lookin' at him.

01:39:31.850 --> 01:39:34.147
Apparently,
you and I are still hitched.

01:39:34.218 --> 01:39:36.118
Is that right?

01:39:39.056 --> 01:39:41.217
Why didn't you tell me
you came to New York?

01:39:41.291 --> 01:39:44.021
I needed to make
somethin' of myself.

01:39:44.094 --> 01:39:45.493
About done?

01:39:47.164 --> 01:39:49.564
What is it
about you Southern girls?

01:39:49.633 --> 01:39:52.458
You can't make the right decisions
'til you tried all the wrong ones?

01:39:52.536 --> 01:39:53.730
At least I fight
for what I want.

01:39:53.804 --> 01:39:55.532
Oh, what do you want, Melanie?

01:39:55.605 --> 01:39:57.971
I don't even think you know.

01:39:58.040 --> 01:40:00.804
You're the first boy
I ever kissed, Jake,...

01:40:00.877 --> 01:40:02.777
and I want you
to be the last.

01:40:02.879 --> 01:40:05.473
Maybe you and I had our chance.

01:40:07.183 --> 01:40:08.309
Fine!

01:40:08.384 --> 01:40:10.477
Have it your way,
you stubborn ass!

01:40:14.257 --> 01:40:17.157
Whatcha want to be
married to me for, anyhow?

01:40:24.332 --> 01:40:26.857
So I can kiss you
any time I want.

01:40:46.053 --> 01:40:48.749
What the hell are you two
tryin' to do...

01:40:48.822 --> 01:40:50.687
get yourselves killed?!

01:40:52.059 --> 01:40:54.391
What seems to be
the trouble, officer?

01:40:54.461 --> 01:40:56.724
I'm here to bring you in,
young lady!

01:40:56.796 --> 01:40:59.287
What did she do this time?

01:40:59.365 --> 01:41:00.764
Well, the way I hear it,...

01:41:00.833 --> 01:41:03.393
seems she run out
on a perfectly good cake.

01:41:24.656 --> 01:41:26.647
You're gettin' a
little light-headed.

01:41:38.903 --> 01:41:41.872
Well, folks, look who finally
made it to their reception...

01:41:41.939 --> 01:41:45.466
Ladies and gentlemen,
Mrs. And Mr. Jake Perry!

01:42:01.558 --> 01:42:05.289
You might want to keep those
for the honeymoon.

01:42:11.434 --> 01:42:15.803
Well... I do believe I owe
this lady a dance.

01:42:15.872 --> 01:42:17.100
You sure do!

01:42:23.912 --> 01:42:25.436
Shut up, Bryant.
